{"tid":1445183,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:37:55.000Z","uid":170136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c0add6488946a9b27960f7fd57f4af1622d176a2","tid":1445183,"uid":170136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 兄弟爬山 各有各做</span></span></strong><br />\n第一個問題<br />\n宜家每日集會最後都會有人俾人拉<br />\n每次出嚟前線就少幾個反觀啲狗冇人受傷<br />\n之前有手足提過嘅兩星期先一次衝突嘅戰術係咪唔可行?<br />\n有人提到唔係前線想衝突 而係啲狗發癲<br />\n咁和理非回合個個星期早少少散水 下個星期先衝突<br />\n多一星期嘅文宣時間會否效果更好?<br />\n最近太多對抗搞到失哂焦<br />\n第二<br />\n遊擊嘅目的唔係要消遣敵人嘅體力?<br />\n要係敵人嚟到之前散水再打另一個地方<br />\n點解好似又變左會定點對抗咁?<br />\n<br />\n前線兄弟唔多 少一個就冇一個 我地要珍惜每一位前線手足<br />\n各位軍師請冷靜討論 前線有前線想法 大家要溝通互相理解勿亂屌<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"40055a88cceec2c9103962835ff2cda4649700bc","tid":1445183,"uid":170136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:04:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f12a808a2a375eaf155cba7d11a1c2111851ba8","tid":1445183,"uid":170136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"799ad5d4af9dfb6488bf9bab4a8cd104dc28b37e","tid":1445183,"uid":170136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"81b22c89095a96d1ddcc8233e9749a90426ec801","tid":1445183,"uid":170136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"2cccbc74ef4f13ee182d5a74807d5b21fdfbca6f","tid":1445183,"uid":170136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"4fcc9e01c77822d7e111d82635b8d28d890fb321","tid"